long_description: servicing residential and commercial clients on the south shore and cape cod. c-mac landscaping offers a wide range of residential landscaping & hardscaping services. providing professional landscaping services & snow removal for commercial properties since 2003. c-mac landscaping, llc is a full service landscaping company based out of south easton, ma. founded in 2003, c-mac serves both residential and commercial properties in the surrounding area. our services range from lawn care, landscape design, construction, to snow plowing. since 1997, c-mac landscaping, llc has been servicing residential and commercial clients on the south shore and cape cod. we aim for long-term relationships with all our clients based on solid trust and loyalty, this can only be achieved by starting with a thorough, honest approach in all communications. listening to our clients requests has been, and remains, a cornerstone of our business philosophy. whether it is conceptual design work, project implementation and construction, or meticulous landscape maintenance and horticultural care, we commit ourselves fully to each and every individual project.
